# Project Context

## Overview

- **Type:** Backend API (NestJS + TypeScript, PostgreSQL)
- **Architecture:** Monolithic modular, stateless, 12-factor app
- **Purpose:** Learning project for AWS deployment (not commercial)

## Principles

- Simplicity over complexity
- Readable code > clever code
- Incremental development (one file at a time)
- No scope creep

## Out of Scope (DO NOT IMPLEMENT)

- Authentication/Authorization
- Frontend/UI
- Cache (Redis)
- Rate limiting
- Custom URLs
- URL expiration
- Advanced analytics

## Development Workflow

1. Never implement features outside PRD
2. Explain approach before generating code
3. Create code incrementally
4. One file at a time
5. Prefer simple solutions
6. No dependencies without justification
7. No dead code
8. No refactoring without explicit request

